'''Aydi''' iga yan anaw n [[Ikzin|iḍan]] ittawsan ɣ umaḍal s yism n "Aydi", ar itzdaɣ d ufgan ɣ tgmmi nns. Aẓur nns iga-tt iẓlmḍ n [[Tafriqt|tfriqt]] zund ukan [[Ayyis amaziɣ]] d [[Askay|uskay]] (slugi). Anaw ad ɣ imudar illa ɣ [[Idrarn n Waṭlas|idrarn n waṭlaṣ]] wahduten akkʷ ɣ umaḍal. Iga Aydi yan wanaw ɣ iḍan bahra idusn ifulkin, iga i tmksawt d tiḍḍaf, ig bahra amkdi. Ar gis ittili 25kg-30kg, tiddi nns nɣ tiɣzi nns ar gis ttili 52cm-62cm, [[Aklu|ikʷlan]] nns iga-tn : awraɣ zund aklu wanas, adman, d usggan

Iga waydi n laṭlas ikzin ittuẓlan s tkssa illa ɣ [[Lmɣrib]] d [[Dzayr]] d [[Tuns]] d ar ittunna mas illa ula ɣ [[Libya]].

Llan iḍan ad ɣ tmazirt nnɣ ɣ idrarn n laṭlas slawann akkʷ aṭlas amjahdi (anammas) macc ittusmagl s ufuḍ s usrag amzwaru a ttigan d umyalwal nns d anawn yiḍan yaḍni. D ar ittddr ɣ unzwi ikʷrmn i ur izzrayn +25 n tskflt d ar ittuẓla waydi yad s wazzar nns iɣzzifn d ukṭṭu ns idusn d udwas ns d usufu ns i bab nsn.

